of such Person prepared in accordance with U.S. GAAP;
(7) all Disqualified Stock issued by such Person, valued at the greater of its voluntary
or involuntary liquidation preference and its maximum fixed repurchase price plus accrued dividends;
or (8) all Preferred Stock issued by a Subsidiary of such Person, valued at the greater of its voluntary
or involuntary liquidation preference and its maximum fixed repurchase price plus accrued dividends;
(9) all Indebtedness of others secured by a Lien on any asset of the specified Person;
(10) to the extent not otherwise included, the Guarantee by the specified Person of any Indebtedness of any other Person.
"
    }
  ]
}

